works.description:
Photographic Template for Photographers to  
create colleges for their clients                       • Designed to be  
displayed as a large canvas of at least 40x40, but is compressed to 20x20,  
300 dpi for faster delivery via download.
• Contains a large template (to hold 45 images) and a small template (to  
hold 25 images).
• Action bundled with this collage makes inserting images fully-automatic,  
saving precious time. Just click play and enjoy the finished product in no  
time!
• Included actions compatible with CS3 or newer.
• Fully layered PSD files for unlimited customization.
• Beautiful linen background.
• Complimentary InDesign file containing both large and small templates for  
speedy drag and drop workflow.
• Vector files may be printed as large as you like.
